name: DS-20-7
content:
DS-20-7 was a TIE pilot of the Galactic Empire.
In 1 ABY DS-20-7 was part of a TIE pilot unit that guarded a statue of Emperor Palpatine installed in front of the Theed Royal Palace on Naboo during that year's Empire Day celebrations.
DS-20-7 appeared in the video game Star Wars Galaxies. He made appearances during the Empire Day live events of 2009.
